segments.text: You have to finish your dinner before you leave the table .
segments.speaker: S1

segments.text: But , Mom , I can't eat anymore . I'm stuffed .
segments.speaker: S2

segments.text: What's the matter ? It doesn't taste good ?
segments.speaker: S1

segments.text: It's not that I don't like your cooking , but I ate some cookies before we had dinner .
segments.speaker: S2
